{"tid":853564,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"比人freeride你會點","createTime":"2018-10-08T16:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T20:00:12.000Z","uid":198369,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7342ba36d650bcb83e7a87c3abfc93e4f535c6de","tid":853564,"uid":198369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:30:32.000Z","msg":"話說我同個friend一齊上堂 <br />\n大家識左半年都OK熟<br />\n就諗住做project同佢一組實冇死<br />\n點能知佢由頭到尾都冇做過野<br />\n但係又不停去蒲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果idea我自己諗能晒<br />\n成個PPT都係我自己做<br />\n聽日就present佢都未知題目係講乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有衝動想同professor報寸<br />\n但係如果佢拎咗0分我驚佢會知道係我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就有排尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該點好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難做但又真係覺得佢好能仆街呀!!!!<br />\n唔想佢同我攞一樣分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6e9960fdcf1b60d80fd9373f7a0b0b77328d40","tid":853564,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:31:36.000Z","msg":"既然係肥絲, 實報!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d875d6a898fa9482c636274c7876c0829d577a3c","tid":853564,"uid":198369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2e6e9960fdcf1b60d80fd9373f7a0b0b77328d40","tid":853564,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:31:36.000Z","msg":"既然係肥絲, 實報!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"佢知道咗咪好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似好賤咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi